title: Estimated Resident Population Change of Michigan Counties: 2010-2012
name: Estimated Resident Population Change of Michigan Counties: 2010-2012
description: The data has the census record for the estimated population of Michigan counties for April 1, 2000 and April 1, 2010. It also has annual estimates from 2010 - 2012. There is also data for the annualized rate of population change and the percent of state population.

author.source: U.S. Census Bureau, Annual Estimates of the Resident Population for Counties of Michigan: 2010-2012. U.S. Census Bureau, Annual Estimates of the Resident Population for Counties of Michigan: 2010-2012.  Release date: March, 2013
